# Reports（本機保留，不公開）
# 用 reports/* 不是 reports/ 因為 git 對 directory ignore 後的 sub-pattern unignore
# 不生效；reports/* 只 ignore 一層內容，允許 !reports/<sub>/ 例外進來
reports/*
# 例外：Phase B0+ pre-registration / decision / audit chain 必入 git
# （hypothesis lock 紀律 — 沒 commit hash anchor 就沒 pre-registered 效力）
!reports/README.md
!reports/phase_b0_lite/
!reports/phase_p5/
!reports/phase_d/
!reports/sprint_pro_validation/
!reports/factor_ic/
!reports/diagnosis/
!reports/architecture_audit_2026_05_02.md

